definitions.definition: Any projection or division , especially one of a somewhat rounded form.
examples: A lobe of lava was crawling down the side of the volcano.

definitions.definition: A clear division of an organ that can be determined at the gross anatomy level, especially one of the parts of the brain , liver or lung .
A semicircular pattern left on the ice as the skater travels across it.

main_definition: Any projection or division , especially one of a somewhat rounded form. [from 19th c.]
secondary_definitions: ( anatomy ) A clear division of an organ that can be determined at the gross anatomy level, especially one of the parts of the brain , liver or lung . [from 16th c.]
( figure skating ) A semicircular pattern left on the ice as the skater travels across it. [from 20th c.]
